  },
  {
   "start": 65.6,
   "end": 67.56,
   "text": "It's better to do it in the morning when you wake up,"
  },
  {
   "start": 67.56,
   "end": 73.04,
   "text": "And you have energy, so I bought two 5-hour energies."
