   "text": "But you should not exceed 2 a day,"
  },
  {
   "start": 82.06,
   "end": 86.24,
   "text": "And you should stagger them by hours, multiples of hours."
  },
  {
   "start": 86.46,
   "end": 89.74,
   "text": "So I just assume they meant, say, 3 hours apart."
  },
  {
   "start": 89.74,
   "end": 95.76,
   "text": "So, like, I'll do a ride, and maybe at the, a few hours in, I'll take one."
  },
  {
   "start": 95.88,
   "end": 98.36,
   "text": "It's just like at night if I get groggy or whatever, I don't know."
  },
  {
   "start": 98.44,
   "end": 102.84,
   "text": "But if I try like a big ride, I'll try those,"
  },
  {
   "start": 102.94,
   "end": 107.74,
   "text": "Just because, you know, I'm not in shape, and I can get groggy."
