  {
   "start": 139.91,
   "end": 141.21,
   "text": "So I was like, all right, let's do this."
  },
  {
   "start": 141.23,
   "end": 143.75,
   "text": "So I got dressed, you know, and I put sunscreen on."
  },
  {
